net.sf.mmm.util.validation.base

Annotation Type Mandatory


  • @Target(value={METHOD,FIELD})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Constraint(validatedBy=MandatoryValidator.class)
public @interface Mandatory
    This is a Constraint for a mandatory field. It is similar to NotNull but with an appropriate message and also considering empty Strings, Collections or Maps.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
